items.body:
We should set the following (copied over from setuptools github):
* long_description_content_type='text/x-rst; charset=UTF-8',
*    ``` project_urls={
        "Documentation": "https://setuptools.readthedocs.io/",
    },```
and set the url to github and the documentation to our homepage. This way we should also see the nice Github statistics on PyPI as with [setuptools](https://pypi.org/project/setuptools/).
